                    <li class="p" value="2">
                        <p>Select the device and log variable to be checked</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p" value="3">
                        <p>Select the operator and enter the comparison constant</p>
                    </li>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>or select the device and the second comparison log variable</p>
                        </li>
